        [![](https://img.shields.io/badge/OS-macOS-blue.svg?longCache=True)]()
        [![](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/mac-terminal-interpreter.svg?maxAge=3600)](https://pypi.org/project/mac-terminal-interpreter/)
